STATE
v.
Julius McLEOD, Jr. No. 600P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2006. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Belinda J. Foster, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th day of October 2005 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 2nd day of March 2006."
